title.narrative: Human Resources for Health (HRH) Capacity Bridge Project

description.narrative: (Kenya): The main goal of the Capacity Bridge mechanism is to strengthen Kenya's Human resources for Health (HRH) systems and capacity at national and county levels to build a sustainable health workforce. Using FY2015 funds, this activity will:1)Support development of devolved human resource management (HRM) policies and strengthen the HRM oversight function of the Ministry of Health at both national and county levels2)Support county HRH management systems, such as workforce forecasting, hiring, distribution, performance, and retention 3) Support USAID contracted health workers and their transition into county government payrolls.
